{
  "stem": "27748.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, after-- I remember we were allowed to visit my father and my brother in the-- after some weeks my mother and I going there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how we went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There must been some sort of-- there were public buses that came through our village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had no other transportation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had bicycles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, after-- again, I'm really guessing-- some two months or so, my father and brother came back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people in the concentration camp, including that farmer and the baker next door, who was also sent to concentration camp, came back after some months.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the baker, when he came back, I couldn't recognize him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I can't-- I couldn't recognize this man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, he had no hair.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't bald the way I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had hair when he left and he had none-- He was shaven, gaunt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His-- his cheeks collapsed, sort of gaunt-looking man, and deep eyes, as though a ghost came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so anyway, what happened in his case was that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when the next roundup came, he committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the pressure to-- I mean, at that point, it was clear that there was no future for us, for Jews, for us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we redoubled our efforts to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think at that point, I suspect my parents made the decision that if they couldn't get out, they would at least try to get me out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's-- I mean, I don't remember somebody saying this, but I felt that was the decision, that-- I mean, we wrote to everybody we could think of about trying to sponsor us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents didn't have the contacts to get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
